#. Description of the plugin
#: rotapress.php
msgid ""
"Editorial rota calendar with role-based access, recurring events, email "
"reminders and personal iCal feed."
msgstr ""
"Calendrier éditorial avec gestion des rôles, événements récurrents, rappels "
"par e-mail et flux iCal personnel."

